; Coverage test for format.cc lines 54-57 (output.cc)
; Tests three-part format (first_line%/next_lines%/between) parsing.
; The third %/ section is the between-format shown between transactions.

2024/01/15 Test1
    Expenses:Food             $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/20 Test2
    Expenses:Gas              $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(date) %(payee) %(account) %(amount)\n%/%(date) cont %(account) %(amount)\n%/---\n'
2024/01/15 Test1 Expenses:Food $50.00
2024/01/15 cont Assets:Cash $-50.00
---
2024/01/20 Test2 Expenses:Gas $30.00
2024/01/20 cont Assets:Cash $-30.00
end test
